— Task Graph\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+# PRD: CypherClaw Humanization — Structured Expression Rendering Layer — Task Graph\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Generated:** 2026-04-16T05:42:58.472070+00:00\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Total tasks:** 25\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Estimated effort:** ~90 hours\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Generated:** 2026-04-16T18:19:25.335643+00:00\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Total tasks:** 40\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Estimated effort:** ~129 hours\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ---\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -10,46 +10,72 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | Order | Task ID | Description | Tier | Complexity | Est (hrs) | Reqs | Deps | Criteria |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n |-------|---------|-------------|------|------------|-----------|------|------|----------|\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| 1 | T-001 | Add dynamics, compression, sidechain, and deference policy. | T1 | 2 | 3 | MPC-010 | — | - production profile maps arc phase to dynamic range, compression intensity, transient policy, and sidechain/deference rules<br/>- Theramini and environmental transients can request generated-material ducking or silence<br/>- tests verify dynamic targets, sidechain metadata, and no over-compression in Divination/Crystallization |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| 2 | T-002 | Add spatial, reverb, and delay production profiles. | T1 | 2 | 3 | MPC-011 | — | - phase profiles define stereo width, near/far depth, reverb size/decay/damping, delay style, and transition-space behavior<br/>- tracker scenes expose spatial intent and reverb/delay sends<br/>- tests verify wide sparse openings, clearer Conversation space, focused Convergence, and long Crystallization tails |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| 3 | T-003 | Complete mastering and loudness policy for